org.jppf.node.protocol

Interface JobCommonSLA

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    JobClientSLA, JobSLA
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractCommonSLA, JPPFJobClientSLA, JPPFJobSLA

    public interface JobCommonSLA
extends Serializable
    This interface represents the Service Level Agreement between a JPPF job and a server. It determines the state, conditions and order in which a job will be executed.
